"通過點擊左上角的齒輪圖示，您可以返回開始畢面。在此畢面的底部將是比賽歷史。"

#: src/components/pages/FairPlayGuidePage.re.mjs:74
msgid "Checkin Screen"
msgstr "簽到畢面"

#: src/components/pages/FairPlayGuidePage.re.mjs:99
msgid "Editing Matches"
